title: [Fireblaze's General Store]
[Fireblaze's Outfitting]
description: The broad sweep of the mahogany floor is interrupted by a twisted iron candlestick.  Halfway to the beam ceiling, a tattered spiderweb hangs on one of the knotty pine walls.  A sooty brass urn and a well-worn wooden rack are pushed close together in the back of the shop.
